{"tid":2045893,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中五男生天台墮下 倒卧學校操場送院亡","createTime":"2020-06-01T05:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T05:37:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5db4fc579baf059ae0b3d195691864c9f75806a6","tid":2045893,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200601/JQGW2O3VUWXH7RFYLWS2VT7JOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200601%2FJQGW2O3VUWXH7RFYLWS2VT7JOQ%2F&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=21e12720\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200601%2FJQGW2O3VUWXH7RFYLWS2VT7JOQ%2F&h=41172c81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200601/JQGW2O3VUWXH7RFYLWS2VT7JOQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n中五男生天台墮下 倒卧學校操場送院亡<br />\n<br />\n【08:34】17歲少年送院經搶救後不治。<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山恆光街香港中國婦女會馮堯敬紀念中學 ，早上6時許，一名身穿校服少年，疑由學校高處墮下，倒卧在操場地上昏迷不醒。附近大廈住客發現有人倒卧，於是報警。救護員趕至現場，立刻替傷者進行急救及將其送往威爾斯醫院搶救，惜最終不治。學校教職員趕到醫院了解事件。據悉，死者為中五男生，他由學校天台墮下，警員於現場沒有撿獲遺書，墮樓原因仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向香港中國婦女會馮堯敬紀念中學查詢有關堕樓事件，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線（多種語言）︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線（24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務）：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGq0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=dd6f5f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n打國際線 《蘋果》英文版免費試睇 按此了解更多<br />\n英文版已登錄新版《蘋果》App按此下載/更新<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 立即WhatsApp《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 或致電：63836568<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5O3EKXQUNZQMLIJUFUTFDUXGN4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5O3EKXQUNZQMLIJUFUTFDUXGN4.jpg&h=1d0448f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員進入學校調查。潘志能攝<br />\n<br />\n一隊探員到學校調查。潘志能攝<br />\n<br />\n少年墮樓送院，警員在醫院調查。周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n警員到學校調查。潘志能攝<br />\n<br />\n學校教職員到醫院了解事件。周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n墮樓<br />\n中學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />